* Serializing and Deserializing of all .NET primitives * Serializing and Deserializing .NET datastructs with interfaces: IList, ICollection, IEnumerable * Serializing and Deserializing .NET Dictionary and IDictionary * Nested Serializing and Deserializing * Support for .NET 3.5, 4.0, 4.5, 4.5.1
